# VERSION
v0.8.0

# Changelog
- v0.8.0
    - **Renamed diagnostics → Transaction Details**
        - Model: `DiagnosticEvent` → `BarDetailEvent`, `diagnostics` → `bar_details`
        - Component renamed to `BacktestBarDetailsComponent` (`app-backtest-bar-details`)
        - Config divider renamed to "Transaction Details"
    - **Transaction Details table improvements**
        - Resizable columns via `nz-resizable` (drag column edges to resize)
        - Shortened action labels: `ORDER_BUY_OK` → `✓ BUY`, `ORDER_SELL_OK` → `✓ SELL`, `ORDER_FAILED` → `✗ FAIL`
        - Added magenta color for `ORDER_FAILED` actions
        - CSV export filename changed to `bar_details_*.csv`
    - **Return Distribution chart** (`return-distribution-chart.component.ts`)
        - Histogram of daily returns with normal distribution overlay
        - Stats panel: Mean, Std Dev, Skewness, Kurtosis (excess), Median, Samples
        - Color-coded skewness/kurtosis values (green/orange/red by severity)
        - Interpretation text box explaining distribution characteristics
        - Available in both Market Data page and Strategy Research page
        - Toggle button to show/hide on demand (default hidden)
    - **Strategy Configuration redesign**
        - Two-section card layout: "Strategy Parameters" and "Data & Capital"
        - Compact CSS Grid fields (4 columns × 160px, no full-width stretching)
        - Vertical label layout (label above input) with 12px labels
        - Bottom bar with Run Backtest button and Transaction Details toggle side by side
    - **Cron Jobs: Fixed active runs navigation**
        - Run ID link: `/cronjobs/run/:id` → `/cronjobs/tasks/:taskId/runs/:runId`
        - Task ID now clickable, linking to task detail page
    - **Industry Explorer page** (`/workbench/industry`)
        - Two search modes: "Industry → Stocks" and "Stock → Industries"
        - Industry hierarchy browser with breadcrumb drill-down navigation
        - Constituent stocks table for selected industry
        - Industry index daily bars table with PE/PB/market cap columns
        - Red/green coloring for close vs pre_close
    - Added Industry API methods to WorkbenchApiService
    - Added industry data model interfaces (IndustryCategory, IndustryConstituent, IndustryDailyBar)
- v0.7.1
    - Fixed bug of displaying mode selection in gridline strategy.
- v0.7.0
    - Added K-Line chart with Buy/Sell signal markers in backtest results (`backtest-kline-chart.component.ts`).
        - Candlestick chart rendered from backtest OHLCV bars data.
        - Green triangle ▲ + "B" label for buy signals, red triangle ▼ + "S" label for sell signals.
        - Includes volume sub-chart and DataZoom.
    - Added Return Rate Curve chart (`return-curve-chart.component.ts`).
        - Percentage Y-axis with green/red coloring based on positive/negative returns.
        - Zero baseline markLine.
    - Updated `BacktestArtifacts` model: added `return_curve: ReturnPoint[]` and `bars?: Bar[]` fields.
    - Updated Research page layout: Stats → K-Line Chart → Equity Curve → Return Curve.
- v0.6.1
    - Propagate response-field renames through workbench.model.ts and workbench-api.service.ts so requests/responses use period and current.
    - Move selected source/dimension state into workbench.store.ts, then simplify market-data.page.ts and strategy-config.component.ts to consume store state without hardcoded fallbacks.
- v0.6.0
    - Added multi-datasource switch in Workbench page.
    - Fixed missing consts in cronjob callback.
    - Added multi-dimension selection in workbench.
- v0.5.1
    - Rename candlestick chart to chart panel.
    - Added break-support line.
    - Added skewness & kurtosis indicators.
    - Fixed overlap charts.
    - Added height control of subcharts.
    - Fixed coexisted scroll bars of charts.
- v0.5.0
    - Added candlestick chart as common component.
    - Added Workbench to research strategy.
    - Added toggle to control Y-axis.
    - Added flexible indicators on candlestick.
- v0.4.2
    - Move cronjob service from common folder to cronjob folder.
- v0.4.1
    - Fixed cronjob "Create based on exists".
- v0.4.0
    - Added a new service in cthulhu project for managing artemis tasks.
      - Tasks register/unregister for dynamic tasks.
      - Tasks add/edit/delete for dynamic tasks.
      - Tasks config management for all tasks.
- v0.3.9
    - Changed cronjob task edit page to support multiple downstream invocations.
- v0.3.8
    - Disable auto jump to task progress and added button to jump to task progress page in cronjob app.
- v0.3.7
    - Extended run detail page of cronjob tasks, fields is rendering with structured format.
- v0.3.6
    - Jump to cronjob progress page after manually triggering a cronjob.
    - Fixed a bug of checking run details in progress page.
- v0.3.5
    - Allowed dev env to be access from any ip.
    - Added deploy script for cthulhu
- v0.3.4
    - Use dropdown list to replace hand-writing input in tast creation page.
    - Fixed error banner not shown issue.
