- v0.3.3
    - Added global error banner and error notifiacation for displaying error message.
- v0.3.2
    - Increased budgets in angular.json
    - Use ip in prod env instead of domain name for backend URL.
    - Changed build cmd in package.json.
- v0.3.1
    - Added page for cronjob progress
    - Fixed a bug of generating breadcrumbs.
